2. You'll see a "Compare & Pull Request" button
â€” click it.

3. Fill in:

â—‹ Title: Add event registration form

â—‹ Description: Added a simple React form
with name, email, and phone fields.

4. Click Create Pull Request

âœ… 5. Review & Merge the PR
Once reviewed:
â— Click "Merge Pull Request"

â— Choose "Squash and merge" for a clean commit
history

â— Click "Delete branch" to keep the repo clean

